flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens Student Progress directory] --> B[Open one student action menu]
    B --> C[Choose Assignment]
    C --> D[Load assignment detail page]
    D --> E{Choose action}
    E -->|Save| F[Update status and feedback]
    E -->|Send Email| G[Send manual assignment email]
    E -->|Delete Video| H[Confirm delete video]
    H --> I{Confirmed?}
    I -->|No| D
    I -->|Yes| J[Clear assignment video]
    F --> K{Approved or Rejected?}
    K -->|Approved| L[Trigger assignment approved email event]
    K -->|Rejected| M[Trigger assignment rejected email event]
    K -->|Other| N[Stay on assignment page]
